    BooleanNormalClause
    either a boolean conjunctive or disjunctive clause represented as a hash set of boolean literals no tautology or contradiction is allowed and it checks implicit tautology like A IS NULL OR (A IS NOT NULL)
    DisjunctiveNormalForm
    this class maintains a CNF or DNF formula, a hash set of BooleanNormalClauses it needs to make sure that none of its normal clause is a tautology or contradiction it checks implicit tautology between clauses like X ISNULL OR X ISNOTNULL
    FixedOrderExpression
    fix the order of expression when the operator does not care about the order for >=,> always turn them into corresponding <,<= make sure this expression representation is unique and hashcode can be computed
